snippet: Stan Wawrinka let his tennis do the talking as he brushed off the after-effects of a cold to breeze into the fourth round of the Australian Open with a 6-2 6-3 7-6(3) victory over Lukas Rosol on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Stan Wawrinka let his tennis do the talking as he brushed off the after-effects of a cold to breeze into the fourth round of the Australian Open with a 6-2 6-3 7-6(3) victory over Lukas Rosol on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Sick but Slick Wawrinka Through to Fourth Round
headline.main: Sick but Slick Wawrinka Through to Fourth Round
